title: Waiting list open at Woodmere Apts - for those 62+ or Disabled
posting_body: ['Get on the waiting list at Woodmere Apartments, a senior/disabled living community.', "You're going to enjoy spending time with your friends in our community room with a cup of coffee, a good book, or a challenging puzzle.", 'In the spring and summer months, step outside to our comfortable outdoor courtyard area, plant a flower or two in our raised beds, or enjoy the birds!', '- Senior Living (62+ or disabled)', '- Now accepting waiting list applications for 1 or 2 BR units', '- 30% of income (income restrictions apply)', '- Recently renovated', '- Next to Senior Center', '- Community room with activities', '- Section 8 Voucher not needed', '- HEAT INCLUDED!', '- No vouchers needed', '- This place feels like home', 'Call Kim for more details at', 'show contact info', '.', 'Equal Housing Opportunity', 'Professionally Managed by Lloyd Management']
